skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: agify me
des: A simple skill for predicting the age of a person given their first name. By telling Alexa your first name, I will try to guess your age based on demographic trends and statistical analytics. I will try to get within a few years of your actual age. But since this is based on statistics, I may not be exact. Care to try? What is your first name?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
